======================================================================
PART 4: T_PURE DELTA-FUNCTION FORMULA
======================================================================
T_pure = sum_k 4*S_a*S_b*(S_a^2 + S_b^2)
= 2*sum_k [cos(k(a-b)) - cos(k(a+b))]*[1 - cos(k(a-b))*cos(k(a+b))]

Expanding and using delta_sum(n) = p-1 if p|n, else -1:
T_pure depends on delta_sum at: a-b, a+b, 3a-b, a-3b, 3a+b, a+3b

